      <h2>Your privacy is under attack</h2>
      <h3>Your personal life, exposed</h3>
      <p>
        Under the proposed data retention laws, records of everything you do online or on your phone would be compulsorily collected and stored.
      </p>
      <p>
        Information about the apps you use, the emails you send, and even the places you go and who you communicate with—all of this data will be collected.
      </p>
    </div>
